➜微“视”驾 | DS 7：谁说法系只是花瓶，实力让你大跌眼镜
http://www.sohu.com/a/432315578_118282	0
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>关注我们</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不可否认，法系品牌在汽车设计上总能让你觉得有些不可思议，似乎它在人们的印象中就是</span>“浪漫”、“不拘一格“的代言词，而作为法系豪华品牌的D </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">S</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>更是如此。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>百听不如一见，此次车厘子小编在试驾</span>D </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">S 7</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>过程中感触颇深，颇具特色的设计让</span>D </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">S 7</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>从内到外都诠释着优雅动感的法系浪漫，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>如果一台</span>DS 7远远朝你开过来，你绝不会把它当做路人一样放过去 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，这是一辆回头率十足的车型。</span></span></p>
<p><strong>外观篇</strong></p>
<p><iframe allowfullscreen="" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=x32048f18cw"></iframe></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>内饰的设计</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>同样可圈可点，除了有豪华的氛围之外，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>无处不在的菱形设计也在散发着它</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>一流的做工和用料</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>越级的高科技配置</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>也让</span>D </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">S 7确实有</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>了</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">“傲慢”的资本。</span></p>
<p><strong>内饰篇</strong></p>
<p><iframe allowfullscreen="" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=q3204pejhwz"></iframe></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>本以为是花瓶，没想到它却是个</span>“西装暴徒“。D </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">S 7</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>搭载了</span>1.6 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">T</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>高低功率两套动力总成，匹配</span>8速手自一体变速箱。配备1.6 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">T</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>高功率发动机的</span>D </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">S 7</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>最大功率可达</span>215匹马力，峰值扭矩为300 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">N</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">·</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">m</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，这样的参数相比</span>2.0 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">T</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>发动机也毫不逊色。</span></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201117/7de4972ffaad41ac80d804e91ef0fa1e.png" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>在底盘调教上</span>D </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">S 7</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>也拥有着越级表现。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">DS <span>魔毯自适应悬架系统可通过实时扫描分析前方路况，并在</span><span>15</span><span>毫秒内</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>预先</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>完成悬架软硬程度的调整，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>即使行驶在颠簸路段，</span>D </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">S7</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>也能完美化解振动，为</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>驾乘</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>者创造如履平地的体验</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span></p>
